commit message: Added to version. Media Button Router in working state, needs UI cleaned up. Doesn't handle Winamp right now because it's BroadcastReceiver is set to the highest possible priority (same as us).

Add timeout to ui. If user doesn't act by timeout, just cancel (finish).
persisting selected index not working.
add comment about wake lock being too late.
Added lock screen specific style, some changes to ui including showing icons, also some work with wakelocks to try and prevent resume pause cycle while display is off. Causes crazy flickering.
add padding between list and other components
shutup text to speech on pause
handle KeyEvent.KEYCODE_MEDIA_STOP by finishing app. Also display text for stop.
don't annouce with tts on config change

Clean up ui so dismiss button always shows and list is constrained. Also prevent resetTimeout from causing exception because executor was already shutdown (didn't affect droid2, only droid og with cm7)
scroll to item in list when moving with media buttons
add preference menu on selector activity
Add conservative option where we don't guess, but let user decide. try to duck the music so the user can decide in piece.  Change messaging from play to pause or play if music is playing.
Don't show options menu when dialog is showing over lock screen.
rename license and notice files to prefered names
manifest not copyrightable, doesn't need header.
